title: Bruce Lehrmann is running out of courts to continue his legal battle
description: With his defamation appeal dismissed and legal costs rising, Bruce Lehrmann is almost out of options. A High Court bid is possible, but what would it take to get there?
content:
Bruce Lehrmann is running out of options, or more specifically, he is running out of courts.
